Package org.letras.ps.rawdata

Interface Summary
IPenAdapter Pen adapters are used by a pen driver to access the logical pen representation.
IPenAdapterFactory A pen adapter factory allows creation of a specific pen adapter.
IPenDriver This interface must be provided by the main class of each pen driver.
 

Class Summary
PenDriverManager The pen driver manager is used to monitor and control the currently installed drivers.
RawDataProcessor The RawDataProcessor is the applications main entry point.
RdpConsole Provides a simple console UI to the raw data processor controlling a Mundo node providing the raw data processing stage in the pipeline.
